{"text_id":194686,"tokens":["Animals"," are"," able"," to"," drink"," water"," from"," puddles",","," dirt"," ponds"," and"," other"," similar"," sources"," because"," of"," their"," immunological"," system"," -"," their"," bodies"," have"," adapted"," to"," thriving"," in"," even"," the"," hars","hest"," environments"," thanks"," to"," their"," genetic"," development",".","\n","The"," digestive"," tracts"," and"," livers"," of"," mammals"," are"," exceptionally"," powerful",","," allowing"," them"," to"," process"," and"," eliminate"," potentially"," harmful"," bacteria"," and"," particles"," from"," their"," water"," supply"," before"," it"," even"," passes"," into"," their"," organ"," tissue","."," The"," saliva"," of"," zoo"," animals"," and"," wild"," predators",","," for"," example",","," is"," full"," of"," antibodies"," that"," help"," to"," neutral","ise"," the"," dangerous"," toxins"," present"," in"," contaminated"," water"," sources","."," This"," type"," of"," immunological"," preparation"," is"," not"," found"," in"," the"," human"," body",","," so"," consuming"," these"," types"," of"," water"," sources"," would"," result"," in"," us"," becoming"," gravely"," ill",".","\n","Animals"," also"," have"," an"," incredibly"," specialised"," set"," of"," metabolic"," processes"," that"," enable"," them"," to"," absorb"," and"," push"," out"," much"," of"," the"," dirt",","," grass"," and"," other"," matter"," from"," their"," water"," sources","."," This"," means"," that"," their"," cells"," are"," constantly"," monitoring"," their"," environment",","," identifying"," and"," eliminating"," any"," potentially"," dangerous"," particles"," before"," they"," can"," even"," make"," it"," into"," their"," bloodstream","."," Again",","," humans"," lack"," these"," metabolic"," processes"," and"," are"," not"," equipped"," to"," handle"," this"," type"," of"," defence"," mechanism",".","\n","As"," a"," result",","," animals"," are"," able"," to"," survive"," drinking"," water"," from"," seemingly"," dirty"," sources",","," while"," humans"," cannot"," do"," the"," same"," without"," risking"," their"," health","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"davinci","label":1}